href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-description\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>aria-description</code></a></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-details\"><code>aria-details</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-disabled\"><code>aria-disabled</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-dropeffect\"><code>aria-dropeffect</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" title=\"Deprecated. Not for use in new websites.\">\n  <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Deprecated</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-errormessage\"><code>aria-errormessage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-expanded\"><code>aria-expanded</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-flowto\"><code>aria-flowto</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-grabbed\"><code>aria-grabbed</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" title=\"Deprecated. Not for use in new websites.\">\n  <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Deprecated</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-haspopup\"><code>aria-haspopup</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-hidden\"><code>aria-hidden</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-invalid\"><code>aria-invalid</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-keyshortcuts\"><code>aria-keyshortcuts</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-label\"><code>aria-label</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-labelledby\"><code>aria-labelledby</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-level\"><code>aria-level</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-live\"><code>aria-live</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-modal\"><code>aria-modal</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-multiline\"><code>aria-multiline</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-multiselectable\"><code>aria-multiselectable</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-orientation\"><code>aria-orientation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-owns\"><code>aria-owns</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-placeholder\"><code>aria-placeholder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-posinset\"><code>aria-posinset</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-pressed\"><code>aria-pressed</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-readonly\"><code>aria-readonly</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-relevant\"><code>aria-relevant</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-required\"><code>aria-required</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-roledescription\"><code>aria-roledescription</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-rowcount\"><code>aria-rowcount</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-rowindex\"><code>aria-rowindex</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-rowindextext\"><code>aria-rowindextext</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-rowspan\"><code>aria-rowspan</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-selected\"><code>aria-selected</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-setsize\"><code>aria-setsize</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-sort\"><code>aria-sort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-valuemax\"><code>aria-valuemax</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-valuemin\"><code>aria-valuemin</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-valuenow\"><code>aria-valuenow</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-valuetext\"><code>aria-valuetext</code></a></li></ol>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The global <code>aria-description</code> attribute defines a string value that describes or annotates the current element.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> <code>aria-description</code> is still in W3C Editor's Draft for ARIA 1.3. For the time being, continue to use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-describedby\"><code>aria-describedby</code></a>, which has been supported since ARIA 1.1.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"Description","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The global <code>aria-description</code> attribute provides a mechanism for the developer to describe or annotate the current element providing greater context for assistive technology users.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">html</span></p><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>application<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-label</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>calendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-description</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Game schedule for the Boston Red Sox 2021 Season<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Red Sox 2021<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>â€¦<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The <code>aria-description</code> attribute is similar to <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-label\"><code>aria-label</code></a> in that both provide a text string to associate with the element, but a label should be short and concise, while the description can be longer as it is intended to provide more context and information.</p>\n<p>The <code>aria-description</code> and <code>aria-describedby</code> properties have the same purpose; both provide the user with additional descriptive text for the object on which it is set. If descriptive text is available in the DOM, use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-describedby\"><code>aria-describedby</code></a> instead.</p>\n<p>The <code>aria-description</code> property should only be used when providing a visible description is not the desired user experience. The <code>aria-describedby</code> attribute takes as its value a list of <code>id</code>s of the elements that contain descriptive text about the object. The <code>aria-description</code> is used when there is no appropriate descriptive text that can be associated with the object by <code>id</code> reference. If both attributes are present, <code>aria-describedby</code> takes precedence in defining the accessible description property.</p>\n<p>The content of the description, whether set by <code>aria-description</code> or <code>aria-describedby</code>, should be flat text. If the content is very long, has semantic meaning requirements, or has a navigational structure, use <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-details\"><code>aria-details</code></a> instead.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"values","title":"Values","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"string\"><a href=\"#string\"><code>&lt;string&gt;</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The value is a string, an unconstrained value type, that is intended to be conveyed to the assistive technology user.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ariamixin_api","title":"ARIAMixin API","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"element.ariadescription\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/ariaDescription\"><code>Element.ariaDescription</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/ariaDescription\"><code>ariaDescription</code></a> property, part of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a> interface, reflects the value of the <code>aria-description</code> attribute, which defines a string value that describes or annotates the current element.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"associated_roles","title":"Associated roles","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Used in <strong>ALL</strong> roles.</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#aria-description","title":"Accessible Rich Internet Applications (WAI-ARIA)"}],"query":"undefined"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See Also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/title\">HTML <code>title</code> attribute</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-describedby\"><code>aria-describedby</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-details\"><code>aria-details</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Description","id":"description"},{"text":"Values","id":"values"},{"text":"ARIAMixin API","id":"ariamixin_api"},{"text":"Associated roles","id":"associated_roles"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"See Also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The global aria-description attribute defines a string value that describes or annotates the current element.","popularity":0.0098,"modified":"2023-04-12T18:48:43.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/accessibility/aria/attributes/aria-description","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/accessibility/aria/attributes/aria-description/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/f6d04a43eadf5ab26a3488942dfb318b58234eb5","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"aria-description","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility","title":"Accessibility"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA","title":"ARIA"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes","title":"ARIA states and properties"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-description","title":"aria-description"}],"pageTitle":"aria-description - Accessibility | MDN","noIndexing":false}}